{"segment":4,"line_start":272,"line_end":360,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_ma_fang_ling","speaker_name":"马芳铃","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"呆子，不该说的时候嘴巴不停，该说的时候反而不说了。","tone":"轻笑","chapter":8,"line_start":272,"line_end":274},{"speaker":"char_ma_fang_ling","speaker_name":"马芳铃","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"今天早上，别人问你昨天晚上在哪里，你为什么不说？","tone":"温柔","chapter":8,"line_start":276,"line_end":278},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_ma_fang_ling","text":"不知道。","tone":"陈述","chapter":8,"line_start":280,"line_end":280},{"speaker":"char_ma_fang_ling","speaker_name":"马芳铃","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"我知道，你是怕连累了我，怕别人说我的闲话，是不是？","tone":"柔声","chapter":8,"line_start":282,"line_end":284},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_ma_fang_ling","text":"不知道。","tone":"陈述","chapter":8,"line_start":286,"line_end":286},{"speaker":"char_ma_fang_ling","speaker_name":"马芳铃","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"你难道不怕他们真的杀了你？","tone":"温柔","chapter":8,"line_start":290,"line_end":290},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_ma_fang_ling","text":"不怕，我只怕你生气。","tone":"温柔","chapter":8,"line_start":292,"line_end":292},{"speaker":"char_ma_fang_ling","speaker_name":"马芳铃","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"我爹爹早上是不是找你谈过话？","tone":"疑问","chapter":8,"line_start":298,"line_end":298},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_ma_fang_ling","text":"嗯。","tone":"陈述","chapter":8,"line_start":300,"line_end":300},{"speaker":"char_ma_fang_ling","speaker_name":"马芳铃","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"他说了些什么？","tone":"疑问","chapter":8,"line_start":302,"line_end":302},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_ma_fang_ling","text":"他要我走，要我离开这地方。","tone":"陈述","chapter":8,"line_start":304,"line_end":304},{"speaker":"char_ma_fang_ling","speaker_name":"马芳铃","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"你说什么？","tone":"疑问","chapter":8,"line_start":306,"line_end":306},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_ma_fang_ling","text":"我不走！","tone":"认真","chapter":8,"line_start":308,"line_end":308},{"speaker":"char_ma_fang_ling","speaker_name":"马芳铃","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"你……你真的不走？","tone":"激动","chapter":8,"line_start":310,"line_end":312},{"speaker":"char_ma_fang_ling","speaker_name":"马芳铃","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"别的地方没人等你。","tone":"温柔","chapter":8,"line_start":316,"line_end":316},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_ma_fang_ling","text":"只有一个地方有人等我。","tone":"柔声","chapter":8,"line_start":318,"line_end":318},{"speaker":"char_ma_fang_ling","speaker_name":"马芳铃","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"哪里？","tone":"疑问","chapter":8,"line_start":320,"line_end":320},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_ma_fang_ling","text":"这里。","tone":"温柔","chapter":8,"line_start":322,"line_end":322},{"speaker":"char_ma_fang_ling","speaker_name":"马芳铃","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"我这一辈子，从来也没有人跟我这样子说过话，从来也没有人拉过我的手……你知不知道？相不相信？","tone":"温柔","chapter":8,"line_start":324,"line_end":326},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_ma_fang_ling","text":"我相信。","tone":"温柔","chapter":8,"line_start":328,"line_end":328},{"speaker":"char_ma_fang_ling","speaker_name":"马芳铃","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"就因为别人都觉得我很凶，所以我自己也越来越觉得自己凶了，其实……","tone":"陈述","chapter":8,"line_start":330,"line_end":330},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_ma_fang_ling","text":"其实你本来就很凶。","tone":"调侃","chapter":8,"line_start":332,"line_end":332},{"speaker":"char_ma_fang_ling","speaker_name":"马芳铃","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"其实有时我跟你生气，根本就是假的。","tone":"微笑","chapter":8,"line_start":334,"line_end":334},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_ma_fang_ling","text":"为什么要假装生气？","tone":"疑问","chapter":8,"line_start":336,"line_end":336},{"speaker":"char_ma_fang_ling","speaker_name":"马芳铃","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"因为……因为我总觉得若不时常发发脾气，别人就会来欺负我。","tone":"犹豫","chapter":8,"line_start":338,"line_end":340},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai"