{"segment":5,"line_start":362,"line_end":462,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_shen_san_niang","speaker_name":"三姨","listener":"char_ma_fang_ling","text":"我们该回去了！","tone":"微笑","chapter":8,"line_start":368,"line_end":368},{"speaker":"char_ma_fang_ling","speaker_name":"马芳铃","listener":"char_shen_san_niang","text":"嗯。","tone":"陈述","chapter":8,"line_start":370,"line_end":370},{"speaker":"char_shen_san_niang","speaker_name":"三姨","listener":"char_ma_fang_ling","text":"我先到外面去等你。","tone":"陈述","chapter":8,"line_start":372,"line_end":372},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_ma_fang_ling","text":"你们每次到镇上，坐的都是那辆马车？","tone":"疑问","chapter":8,"line_start":386,"line_end":388},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_ma_fang_ling","text":"像那样的马车，你们一共有几辆？","tone":"疑问","chapter":8,"line_start":392,"line_end":392},{"speaker":"char_ma_fang_ling","speaker_name":"马芳铃","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"只有一辆。这里的人，都比较喜欢骑马。","tone":"陈述","chapter":8,"line_start":394,"line_end":394},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_ma_fang_ling","text":"就因为你们要坐这辆马车，所以他们就只能自己回来了。","tone":"无奈","chapter":8,"line_start":396,"line_end":398},{"speaker":"char_ma_fang_ling","speaker_name":"马芳铃","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"他们是谁？","tone":"疑问","chapter":8,"line_start":400,"line_end":400},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_ma_fang_ling","text":"昨天晚上跟我一起去的客人。","tone":"陈述","chapter":8,"line_start":402,"line_end":402},{"speaker":"char_ma_fang_ling","speaker_name":"马芳铃","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"他们又不是孩子了，自己回来又有什么关系？你又何必叹气？","tone":"轻笑","chapter":8,"line_start":404,"line_end":406},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_ma_fang_ling","text":"因为他们十三个人来，现在已死了一个，不见了十一个。","tone":"无奈","chapter":8,"line_start":408,"line_end":410},{"speaker":"char_ma_fang_ling","speaker_name":"马芳铃","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"死的是谁？","tone":"疑问","chapter":8,"line_start":412,"line_end":412},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_ma_fang_ling","text":"飞天蜘蛛。","tone":"陈述","chapter":8,"line_start":414,"line_end":414},{"speaker":"char_ma_fang_ling","speaker_name":"马芳铃","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"不见了的呢？","tone":"疑问","chapter":8,"line_start":416,"line_end":416},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_ma_fang_ling","text":"乐大先生、慕容明珠，和他那九个跟班的。","tone":"陈述","chapter":8,"line_start":418,"line_end":418},{"speaker":"char_ma_fang_ling","speaker_name":"马芳铃","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"这么大的人了，怎么会不见呢？","tone":"疑问","chapter":8,"line_start":420,"line_end":420},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_ma_fang_ling","text":"这地方本来就随时都会有怪事发生的。","tone":"陈述","chapter":8,"line_start":422,"line_end":422},{"speaker":"char_ma_fang_ling","speaker_name":"马芳铃","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"也许这只不过是你的疑心病，他们说不定很快就会回来的。","tone":"微笑","chapter":8,"line_start":424,"line_end":426},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_ma_fang_ling","text":"我能不能顺便搭你们的马车到前面去？","tone":"疑问","chapter":8,"line_start":428,"line_end":428},{"speaker":"char_ma_fang_ling","speaker_name":"马芳铃","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"当然可以。只不过……你到前面去干什么呢？","tone":"疑问","chapter":8,"line_start":430,"line_end":430},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_ma_fang_ling","text":"去找那些不见了的人。","tone":"陈述","chapter":8,"line_start":432,"line_end":432},{"speaker":"char_ma_fang_ling","speaker_name":"马芳铃","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"你怎么知道他们还在附近？也许他们从别的路回去了呢？","tone":"疑问","chapter":8,"line_start":434,"line_end":436},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_ma_fang_ling","text":"不会的。","tone":"陈述","chapter":8,"line_start":438,"line_end":438},{"speaker":"char_ma_fang_ling","speaker_name":"马芳铃","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"为什么不会？","tone":"疑问","chapter":8,"line_start":440,"line_end":440},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_ma_fang_ling","text":"我知道。","tone":"陈述","chapter":8,"line_start":442,"line_end":442},{"speaker":"char_ma_fang_ling","speaker_name":"马芳铃","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"怎么知道的？","tone":"疑问","chapter":8,"line_start":444,"line_end":444},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_ma_fang_ling","text":"有人告诉我。","tone":"陈述","chapter":8,"line_start":446,"line_end":446},{"speaker":"char_ma_fang_ling","speaker_name":"马芳铃","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"是什么人告诉你的？","tone":"疑问","chapter":8,"line_start":448,"line_end":448},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_ma_fang_ling","text":"是个死人……","tone":"陈述","chapter":8,"line_start":450,"line_end":450},{"speaker":"char_ma_fang_ling","speaker_name":"马芳铃","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"死人？","tone":"惊讶","chapter":8,"line_start":452,"line_end":452},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_ma_fang_ling","text":"你知不知道，死人有时也会说话的，只不过他们说话的方法和活人不同而已。","tone":"陈述","chapter":8,"line_start":454,"line_end":456},{"speaker":"char_ma_fang_ling","speaker_name":"马芳铃","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"死人说的话你也相信？","tone":"惊讶","chapter":8,"line_start":458,"line_end":458},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_ma_fang_ling","text":"只有死人告诉你的事，才永远不会是假的……因为他已根本不必骗你。","tone":"陈述","chapter":8,"line_start":460,"line_end":462}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_ma_kong_qun","name":"马空群","alias":[],"identity":"万马堂堂主","faction":"万马堂","role":"villain","archetype":"warrior","rank":"登峰造极","one_line":"洞察死者双手线索并判断飞天蜘蛛之死与复仇者有关。","personality":{"traits":["沉稳","威严","精明","多疑","深藏恐惧","善控下属"],"speech_style":"缓慢笃定，命令简短有压迫感","temperament":"威严而阴沉"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[8],"source_refs":[{"chapter":8,"line_start":468,"line_end":490,"text":"马空群站在棺材旁，目光灼灼，盯着这双手。 他既不看这死人扭曲变形的脸，也不看那嘴角凝结了的血渍，只是盯着这双手。 所以每个人都在盯着这双手。 马空群忽然道：\"你们看出了什么？\" 花满天和云在天对望了一眼，沉默着。 公孙断道：\"这只不过是双死"}]},{"id":"char_hua_man_tian","name":"花满天","alias":[],"identity":"万马堂人物","faction":"万马堂","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"炉火纯青","one_line":"在马空群查验尸体时旁观沉默。","personality":{"traits":["沉默","稳重","谨慎","江湖经验深","服从大局"],"speech_style":"本章未直接开口","temperament":"沉静谨慎"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[8],"source_refs":[{"chapter":8,"line_start":476,"line_end":476,"text":"花满天和云在天对望了一眼，沉默着。"}]}],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[{"id":"char_ye_kai","updates":{"source_refs":[{"chapter":8,"line_start":386,"line_end":462,"text":"叶开当然不能将这种感觉露出来，所以忽然问道：\"你们每次到镇上，坐的都是那辆马车？ \" 马芳铃显然不明白他为什么要问这句话，但还是点了点头。 叶开道：\"像那样的马车，你们一共有几辆？\" 马芳铃道：\"只有一辆。这里的人，都比较喜欢骑马。\" 叶开"}],"one_line":"叶开由飞天蜘蛛之死推断失踪者仍在附近，并准备追查。"},"relationship_updates":[]},{"id":"char_ma_fang_ling","updates":{"source_refs":[{"chapter":8,"line_start":386,"line_end":458,"text":"叶开当然不能将这种感觉露出来，所以忽然问道：\"你们每次到镇上，坐的都是那辆马车？ \" 马芳铃显然不明白他为什么要问这句话，但还是点了点头。 叶开道：\"像那样的马车，你们一共有几辆？\" 马芳铃道：\"只有一辆。这里的人，都比较喜欢骑马。\" 叶开"}]},"relationship_updates":[]},{"id":"char_fei_tian_zhi_zhu","updates":{"source_refs":[{"chapter":8,"line_start":450,"line_end":462,"text":"叶开垂头看着自己的手，一字字地说道：\"是个死人……\" 马芳铃骇然道：\"死人？\" 叶开点了点头，缓缓道：\"你知不知道，死人有时也会说话的，只不过他们说话的方法和活人不同而已。 \" 马芳铃吃惊地看着他，讷讷道：\"死人说的话你也相信？\" 叶开又点"}],"one_line":"飞天蜘蛛的死亡被叶开视为能说话的线索。"},"relationship_updates":[]}]}
{"segment":6,"line_start":464,"line_end":630,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":null,"text":"你们看出了什么？","tone":"疑问","chapter":8,"line_start":474,"line_end":474},{"speaker":"char_gong_sun_duan","speaker_name":"公孙断","listener":"char_ma_kong_qun","text":"这只不过是双死人的手，和别的死人并没有什么地方不同。","tone":"陈述","chapter":8,"line_start":478,"line_end":480},{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":"char_gong_sun_duan","text":"有。","tone":"陈述","chapter":8,"line_start":482,"line_end":482},{"speaker":"char_gong_sun_duan","speaker_name":"公孙断","listener":"char_ma_kong_qun","text":"有什么不同？","tone":"疑问","chapter":8,"line_start":484,"line_end":484},{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":"char_gong_sun_duan","text":"这双手本来握得很紧，后来才被人扳开来的。","tone":"陈述","chapter":8,"line_start":486,"line_end":486},{"speaker":"char_gong_sun_duan","speaker_name":"公孙断","listener":"char_ma_kong_qun","text":"你看得出？","tone":"疑问","chapter":8,"line_start":488,"line_end":488},{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":"char_gong_sun_duan","text":"死人的骨头和血已冷硬，想扳开死人的手并不容易，所以他的手指才会这样子扭曲，而且上面还有伤痕。","tone":"陈述","chapter":8,"line_start":490,"line_end":492},{"speaker":"char_gong_sun_duan","speaker_name":"公孙断","listener":"char_ma_kong_qun","text":"也许是他临死前受的伤。","tone":"陈述","chapter":8,"line_start":494,"line_end":494},{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":"char_gong_sun_duan","text":"绝不是。","tone":"陈述","chapter":8,"line_start":496,"line_end":496},{"speaker":"char_gong_sun_duan","speaker_name":"公孙断","listener":"char_ma_kong_qun","text":"为什么？","tone":"疑问","chapter":8,"line_start":498,"line_end":498},{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":"char_gong_sun_duan","text":"因为若是生前受的伤，伤口一定有血渍，只有死了很久的人才不会流血。","tone":"陈述","chapter":8,"line_start":500,"line_end":502},{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":"char_yun_zai_tian","text":"你看见这尸体时，他是不是已死了很久？","tone":"疑问","chapter":8,"line_start":504,"line_end":506},{"speaker":"char_yun_zai_tian","speaker_name":"云在天","listener":"char_ma_kong_qun","text":"至少已死了一个时辰，因为那时他的人已冷透。","tone":"陈述","chapter":8,"line_start":508,"line_end":510},{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":"char_yun_zai_tian","text":"那时他的手呢？是不是握得很紧？","tone":"疑问","chapter":8,"line_start":512,"line_end":512},{"speaker":"char_yun_zai_tian","speaker_name":"云在天","listener":"char_ma_kong_qun","text":"那时我没有留意他的手。","tone":"犹豫","chapter":8,"line_start":514,"line_end":514},{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":"char_yun_zai_tian","text":"那时你留意着什么？","tone":"冷酷","chapter":8,"line_start":516,"line_end":516},{"speaker":"char_yun_zai_tian","speaker_name":"云在天","listener":"char_ma_kong_qun","text":"我……我正急着去盘问别的人。","tone":"犹豫","chapter":8,"line_start":518,"line_end":518},{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":"char_yun_zai_tian","text":"你问出了什么？","tone":"疑问","chapter":8,"line_start":520,"line_end":520},{"speaker":"char_yun_zai_tian","speaker_name":"云在天","listener":"char_ma_kong_qun","text":"没有。","tone":"陈述","chapter":8,"line_start":522,"line_end":522},{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":"char_yun_zai_tian","text":"下次你最好记得，死人能告诉你的事，也许比活人还多，而且也远比活人可靠。","tone":"沉声","chapter":8,"line_start":524,"line_end":526},{"speaker":"char_yun_zai_tian","speaker_name":"云在天","listener":"char_ma_kong_qun","text":"是。","tone":"陈述","chapter":8,"line_start":528,"line_end":528},{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":"char_yun_zai_tian","text":"他这双手里，必定紧握一样东西，这样东西必定是个很重要的线索，说不定就是他从凶手身上抓下来的，当时你若找出了这样东西，现在我们说不定就已知道凶手是谁了。","tone":"陈述","chapter":8,"line_start":530,"line_end":532},{"speaker":"char_yun_zai_tian","speaker_name":"云在天","listener":"char_ma_kong_qun","text":"下次我一定留意。","tone":"陈述","chapter":8,"line_start":534,"line_end":534},{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":"char_yun_zai_tian","text":"当时除了你之外，还有谁在这口棺材附近？","tone":"疑问","chapter":8,"line_start":536,"line_end":538},{"speaker":"char_yun_zai_tian","speaker_name":"云在天","listener":"char_ma_kong_qun","text":"还有叶开！","tone":"激动","chapter":8,"line_start":540,"line_end":540},{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":"char_yun_zai_tian","text":"你有没有看见他动过这尸体？","tone":"疑问","chapter":8,"line_start":542,"line_end":542},{"speaker":"char_yun_zai_tian","speaker_name":"云在天","listener":"char_ma_kong_qun","text":"我也没有留意，只不过……","tone":"犹豫","chapter":8,"line_start":544,"line_end":544},{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":"char_yun_zai_tian","text":"只不过怎样？","tone":"疑问","chapter":8,"line_start":546,"line_end":546},{"speaker":"char_yun_zai_tian","speaker_name":"云在天","listener":"char_ma_kong_qun","text":"只不过他对这尸体，好像也很有兴趣，站在棺材旁看了很久。","tone":"陈述","chapter":8,"line_start":548,"line_end":550},{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":null,"text":"这少年看出的事，只怕远比想的多得多。","tone":"冷笑","chapter":8,"line_start":552,"line_end":552},{"speaker":"char_gong_sun_duan","speaker_name":"公孙断","listener":"char_ma_kong_qun","text":"这人只不过是个飞贼，他是死是活，和我们有什么关系？","tone":"疑问","chapter":8,"line_start":554,"line_end":556},{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":"char_gong_sun_duan","text":"有。","tone":"陈述","chapter":8,"line_start":558,"line_end":558},{"speaker":"char_gong_sun_duan","speaker_name":"公孙断","listener":"char_ma_kong_qun","text":"有关系？","tone":"疑问","chapter":8,"line_start":560,"line_end":560},{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":"char_gong_sun_duan","text":"这人虽是个飞贼，却是个最精明的飞贼，只要一出手，必定万无一失，可见他对别人的观察必是十分准确仔细。","tone":"陈述","chapter":8,"line_start":562,"line_end":564},{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":"char_gong_sun_duan","text":"所以，我才特地叫人找他到这里来……","tone":"陈述","chapter":8,"line_start":566,"line_end":566},{"speaker":"char_gong_sun_duan","speaker_name":"公孙断","listener":"char_ma_kong_qun","text":"这人是你特地找来的？","tone":"惊讶","chapter":8,"line_start":568,"line_end":568},{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":"char_gong_sun_duan","text":"是我花了五千两银子请来的。","tone":"沉声","chapter":8,"line_start":570,"line_end":570},{"speaker":"char_gong_sun_duan","speaker_name":"公孙断","listener":"char_ma_kong_qun","text":"请他来干什么？","tone":"疑问","chapter":8,"line_start":572,"line_end":572},{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":"char_gong_sun_duan","text":"请他来替我在暗中侦查，谁是来寻仇的人。","tone":"陈述","chapter":8,"line_start":574,"line_end":574},{"speaker":"char_gong_sun_duan","speaker_name":"公孙断","listener":"char_ma_kong_qun","text":"为什么要找他？","tone":"疑问","chapter":8,"line_start":576,"line_end":576},{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":"char_gong_sun_duan","text":"因为他和这件事全没有关系，别人对他的警戒自然就比较疏忽，他查出真相的机会，自然也比较多。","tone":"陈述","chapter":8,"line_start":578,"line_end":580},{"speaker":"char_gong_sun_duan","speaker_name":"公孙断","listener":"char_ma_kong_qun","text":"只可惜他什么也没有查出来，就已死了。","tone":"无奈","chapter":8,"line_start":582,"line_end":582},{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":"char_gong_sun_duan","text":"他若什么都没有查出来，就不会死！","tone":"沉声","chapter":8,"line_start":584,"line_end":584},{"speaker":"char_gong_sun_duan","speaker_name":"公孙断","listener":"char_ma_kong_qun","text":"哦？","tone":"疑问","chapter":8,"line_start":586,"line_end":586},{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":"char_gong_sun_duan","text":"就因为他已发现了那凶手的秘密，所以才会被人杀了灭口！","tone":"陈述","chapter":8,"line_start":588,"line_end":590},{"speaker":"char_gong_sun_duan","speaker_name":"公孙断","listener":"char_ma_kong_qun","text":"所以我们只要找出是谁杀他的，就可以知道谁是来找我们麻烦的人了。","tone":"惊讶","chapter":8,"line_start":592,"line_end":594},{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":"char_gong_sun_duan","text":"所以他手里握着的线索，关系才如此重要！","tone":"冷酷","chapter":8,"line_start":596,"line_end":596},{"speaker":"char_gong_sun_duan","speaker_name":"公孙断","listener":"char_ma_kong_qun","text":"我去问问叶开，那东西是不是他拿走的？","tone":"陈述","chapter":8,"line_start":598,"line_end":598},{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":"char_gong_sun_duan","text":"不必。","tone":"陈述","chapter":8,"line_start":600,"line_end":600},{"speaker":"char_gong_sun_duan","speaker_name":"公孙断","listener":"char_ma_kong_qun","text":"为什么？","tone":"疑问","chapter":8,"line_start":602,"line_end":602},{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":"char_gong_sun_duan","text":"他死的时候，叶开在镇上，所以杀他的凶手绝不是叶开。","tone":"陈述","chapter":8,"line_start":604,"line_end":606},{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":"char_gong_sun_duan","text":"何况，叶开若真从他手上拿走了什么，也没有人能问得出来。","tone":"冷酷","chapter":8,"line_start":608,"line_end":610},{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":"char_yun_zai_tian","text":"他临死之前，是谁跟他在一起的？","tone":"疑问","chapter":8,"line_start":614,"line_end":614},{"speaker":"char_yun_zai_tian","speaker_name":"云在天","listener":"char_ma_kong_qun","text":"乐大先生、慕容明珠、傅红雪。","tone":"陈述","chapter":8,"line_start":616,"line_end":616},{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":"char_yun_zai_tian","text":"现在他们的人呢？","tone":"疑问","chapter":8,"line_start":618,"line_end":618},{"speaker":"char_yun_zai_tian","speaker_name":"云在天","listener":"char_ma_kong_qun","text":"傅红雪已回到镇上，乐乐山和慕容明珠却已失踪了。","tone":"陈述","chapter":8,"line_start":620,"line_end":620},{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":"char_yun_zai_tian","text":"去找他们，带四十个人去找。","tone":"冷酷","chapter":8,"line_start":622,"line_end":622},{"speaker":"char_yun_zai_tian","speaker_name":"云在天","listener":"char_ma_kong_qun","text":"是。","tone":"陈述","chapter":8,"line_start":624,"line_end":624},{"speaker":"char_ma_kong_qun","speaker_name":"马空群","listener":"char_yun_zai_tian","text":"十个人一组，分成四组，多带食水口粮，找不到线索就不许回来！","tone":"厉声","chapter":8,"line_start":626,"line_end":628},{"speaker":"char_yun_zai_tian","speaker_name":"云在天","listener":"char_ma_kong_qun","text":"是。","tone":"陈述","chapter":8,"line_start":630,"line_end":630}],"new_entities":{"characte